Title: Fix confirm message of remove comment command
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1622043104
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

If you wanted to remove a comment, e.g. for a service, the confirm message was
"Do you really want to remove the following x services".

The command was only executed for the comment, no hosts or services were lost.
